
0. Linux
    curl https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py -o get-pip.py
    python get-pip.py

1. download get-pip.py
    wget https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py

2. Upgrading pip
    On Linux or macOS:
        pip install -U pip
    On Windows:
        python -m pip install -U pip
3. sudo pip install virtualenv